headline: Defying Convention to Deepen Connections: Booking.com's Nine Predictions for Travel in 2025
summary: Booking.com's annual Travel Predictions research* reveals how Australian travellers are 'rewriting the playbook' in 2025 by defying the rules of conventional getaways and as a result, forging new connections with themselves, their loved ones, those they meet along the way, as well as the destinations they visit.
